[
  {
    "key": "9bcf69da12a41765f7bfba0a8e2511617a4a8a471555042c60fac518b0b2e366",
    "original": "%name% has apparently been in many militias, all of which eventually dissolved for one reason or another. At no point has he made any money in any of them, so he hopes to changes that with this whole new sellswording schtick.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "bros[7].getBackground().m.RawDescription = \"%name% has apparently been in many militias, all of which eventually dissolved for one reason or another. At no point has he made any money in any of them, so he hopes to changes that with this whole new sellswording schtick.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "e4746f9f6441d37cb49fc7dcc965e97c88e0030be2bad8c69c113ff2ee865700",
    "original": "%name% is a farmer's son, and presumably wishes to be the father of his own son at some point. For now, he's with you which is quite a regrettable clash between dreams and reality.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "bros[0].getBackground().m.RawDescription = \"%name% is a farmer's son, and presumably wishes to be the father of his own son at some point. For now, he's with you which is quite a regrettable clash between dreams and reality.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "ebfd8107f0ffdb5f6ff0c58aaadcce06edd484f462ca5fc6df9fbfb83a7ab9e7",
    "original": "%name% is, ostensibly, running away from his wife. You met her once and approve his escape plan entirely, and not just because it affords you another body on the front line.That wench is genuinely crazy.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "bros[11].getBackground().m.RawDescription = \"%name% is, ostensibly, running away from his wife. You met her once and approve his escape plan entirely, and not just because it affords you another body on the front line.That wench is genuinely crazy.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "fc0c86b72efb5ff0d6303e5b171c60c21cec250fc0fe71c20593a8ffd2920c7c",
    "original": "%name% owned a farmstead that has long since gone underfoot of countless passing armies, including the very ones he has fought for. His 'allegiance' to you is arguably the result of an empty belly more than anything.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "bros[1].getBackground().m.RawDescription = \"%name% owned a farmstead that has long since gone underfoot of countless passing armies, including the very ones he has fought for. His 'allegiance' to you is arguably the result of an empty belly more than anything.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "674617632420c81ccb2fd8b7a16826698fa7f710a48cc389c633e6436d90347d",
    "original": "%name% states he was a sailor prior to coming inland and falling in with the militia and now your mercenary band. He hopes to eventually own a boat and put its sails to the open ocean. You hope he can do that someday, truly.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "bros[6].getBackground().m.RawDescription = \"%name% states he was a sailor prior to coming inland and falling in with the militia and now your mercenary band. He hopes to eventually own a boat and put its sails to the open ocean. You hope he can do that someday, truly.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "d2b61d851478e67bfbc3b8d0c19178e96ed4be0362e8793cd5c1542f89437df7",
    "original": "A daytaler and common laborer, %name% would rather join your outfit than go back to wasting his body building some nobleman's new fancy foyer.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "bros[4].getBackground().m.RawDescription = \"A daytaler and common laborer, %name% would rather join your outfit than go back to wasting his body building some nobleman's new fancy foyer.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "4762cbac707591c7dc9a11da7a5df94af9b80e7bdf3fa38ffd6abdb5f9a6f2a6",
    "original": "A proper lad, %name% enjoys carousing ladies at the pub and chasing skirt in the church. You get the sense he's only tagged along to spread his sense of 'fun' around the world.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "bros[8].getBackground().m.RawDescription = \"A proper lad, %name% enjoys carousing ladies at the pub and chasing skirt in the church. You get the sense he's only tagged along to spread his sense of 'fun' around the world.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "4ba0023d81662c419bcb20504506d4281a5e9699dcab75fb9da412e195755f45",
    "original": "Considered local heroes for keeping the village safe",
    "translation": "",
    "context": ""
  },
  {
    "key": "ba8f9a54db29dc1b9ea476d11ece8563fedb6b90e700c81191299c3d2d3b7a91",
    "original": "Daytaler, laborer, caravan hand, sailor, militiaman, %name%'s done a bit of it all. Hopefully this new foray into mercenary work will stick for him.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "bros[9].getBackground().m.RawDescription = \"Daytaler, laborer, caravan hand, sailor, militiaman, %name%'s done a bit of it all. Hopefully this new foray into mercenary work will stick for him.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "69291b6adb355cf8925464c433eccc768196103358810caad31a40a60bd9dc59",
    "original": "Disliked that some members of the militia were involved in a brawl",
    "translation": "",
    "context": ""
  },
  {
    "key": "72189ed57c95b59a74054f874f060cf59b5d379c9fda56e294348a43536d39a6",
    "original": "Feels somewhat sickly of late",
    "translation": "",
    "context": ""
  },
  {
    "key": "b3d7886c9ad2831f1437f81bcc463b3c8e7bfeb739a8db0651a14483df9a0b0b",
    "original": "Had his trusty scramasax stolen",
    "translation": "",
    "context": ""
  },
  {
    "key": "f7b2cd8ac6664c546b58a7a16601941c7c2265b0ae312115521e1bb6427b4884",
    "original": "Has recently become a father",
    "translation": "",
    "context": ""
  },
  {
    "key": "69285420b759a314d1870b4989bad1dfa407960fa8410e44d79f64c551aee1e5",
    "original": "Has recently fallen in love",
    "translation": "",
    "context": ""
  },
  {
    "key": "a2c4ec34b03ed6dc5d4b5128843f8b7a9a22b2e6b41f67b829eacb469bbb3212",
    "original": "It is a common joke that %name% is in fact a nobleman hiding away from the world, but to the best of your knowledge he was a simple poacher. The grind of the world got him to where he is today, not much else need be said other than you hope he gets back on his feet.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "bros[2].getBackground().m.RawDescription = \"It is a common joke that %name% is in fact a nobleman hiding away from the world, but to the best of your knowledge he was a simple poacher. The grind of the world got him to where he is today, not much else need be said other than you hope he gets back on his feet.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "819852f06916526cdfd923344869a2f122d9ae004b538d077dada4b79ee0ca26",
    "original": "Like yourself, %name% was fed up with militias being overused to solve the crises of unprepared nobles. He was arguably the most earnest of the men in joining the transition to mercenary work.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "bros[10].getBackground().m.RawDescription = \"Like yourself, %name% was fed up with militias being overused to solve the crises of unprepared nobles. He was arguably the most earnest of the men in joining the transition to mercenary work.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "79cdfe850d10f827aa067c9f27ca4a91a16b42c632e5d5f697b66ca933674dcc",
    "original": "Looks forward to becoming rich as a sellsword",
    "translation": "",
    "context": ""
  },
  {
    "key": "b0d50b2a40e20351db27651e3bbdfd15916145f34dac198873fa6d544f9b77b5",
    "original": "Lost many a friend in battle",
    "translation": "",
    "context": ""
  },
  {
    "key": "45ba2ba167984368ced31fa011776717e3ade69a4b00ed04d07252c4e6e2c9ef",
    "original": "Managed to get away from his wife",
    "translation": "",
    "context": ""
  },
  {
    "key": "dd9a33684c579907f5619b1c525ec45c5adca3620011b0439106c25c745e5f2e",
    "original": "Part of a militia",
    "translation": "",
    "context": ""
  },
  {
    "key": "63b1706380aff81d4278d2779ba4efcac5dac3dfa784ae1f7fce9e71e48860f0",
    "original": "Peasant Militia",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "this.m.Name = \"Peasant Militia\""
  },
  {
    "key": "6ccfecd93ae08c47344ff96bd757857216b9c92a740733eb71dd6a88926e19b4",
    "original": "Seeking riches, %name% has come to the right place in your newfound mercenary band. Unfortunately, his background is in farming, milling, and laying stone, particularly none of which he was any good at.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "bros[5].getBackground().m.RawDescription = \"Seeking riches, %name% has come to the right place in your newfound mercenary band. Unfortunately, his background is in farming, milling, and laying stone, particularly none of which he was any good at.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "6435d5731f14e33bf04ead46fbf1831baac5f2bdcef2148821e2fb27cf79a3a7",
    "original": "Stole someone's scramasax",
    "translation": "",
    "context": ""
  },
  {
    "key": "0490256d9ed01025c16b0880e8f86253c8560972ea7232b6bb9ea63347228513",
    "original": "Was involved in a brawl",
    "translation": "",
    "context": ""
  },
  {
    "key": "69851c33441cc7a30e0c4694cabd6f31235f5c34f06195253fbebe50446a3cef",
    "original": "You notice that %name% hides from certain noblemen. It is likely that he is a common criminal at large for some petty crime, but so long as he fights well it is no business to you.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "bros[3].getBackground().m.RawDescription = \"You notice that %name% hides from certain noblemen. It is likely that he is a common criminal at large for some petty crime, but so long as he fights well it is no business to you.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "49fec99bae6446dd0e89d406e71710259f9a5b072a126d11fb090c023bed2e52",
    "original": "[p=c][img]gfx/ui/events/event_141.png[/img][/p][p]It started as a ragtag militia made up of anyone brave or desperate enough to volunteer for defending their homes, but has grown into a small army. An army that needs to be fed each day. Perhaps the militia's services could be rented out?\n\n[color=#bcad8c]Peasant Army:[/color] Start with a roster of 12 poorly equipped peasants.\n[color=#bcad8c]Human Wave[/color]: Take up to 16 men into battle at once, and have up to 25 in your roster.\n[color=#bcad8c]Dirty Peasants[/color]: Can never hire anyone that isn't a lowborn peasant.[/p]",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "this.m.Description = \"[p=c][img]gfx/ui/events/event_141.png[/img][/p][p]It started as a ragtag militia made up of anyone brave or desperate enough to volunteer for defending their homes, but has grown into a small army. An army that needs to be fed each day. Perhaps the militia's services could be rented out?\\n\\n[color=#bcad8c]Peasant Army:[/color] Start with a roster of 12 poorly equipped peasants.\\n[color=#bcad8c]Human Wave[/color]: Take up to 16 men into battle at once, and have up to 25 in your roster.\\n[color=#bcad8c]Dirty Peasants[/color]: Can never hire anyone that isn't a lowborn peasant.[/p]\""
  }
]